            VeriFone Systems Inc. is one of the leading providers of secure electronic payment solutions. The company offers various solutions and services for the financial, retail, hospitality, petroleum, government and health care markets. Its product line includes point-of-sale software and terminals, smart card and check readers, receipt printers and Internet commerce software. The company also generates sales from installation, project management, training and other services. Its system solutions process a variety of payment types, including signature and personal identification number-based debit, credit and radio frequency identification cards. The company also offers a wide range of electronic bill payment, check authorization and conversion, signature capture and electronic benefits transfer solutions. VeriFone Systems is located in San Jose, Calif.
          






















